    "Sudhina Kumar et al.",
    "This model is integrated with joint announcement protocols to reduce communication overhead and enhance system resilience.",
    "In contrast, Aouedi et al. (2022b) deployed the same model to address challenges such as privacy concerns, bandwidth overhead, and the need for extensive labeled data in 5 G and beyond networks.",
